{"tid":930572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本新天皇5月1日即位　首個會見外國元首將是特朗普","createTime":"2018-12-06T11:45:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T00:52:14.000Z","uid":141151,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f63ee0458fd53b95f82d6eb9a3d0211b1b4dd1b6","tid":930572,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T11:45:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">日本新天皇5月1日即位　首個會見外國元首將是特朗普</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/267879/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%96%B0%E5%A4%A9%E7%9A%875%E6%9C%881%E6%97%A5%E5%8D%B3%E4%BD%8D-%E9%A6%96%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%83%E8%A6%8B%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%83%E9%A6%96%E5%B0%87%E6%98%AF%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F267879%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E7%259A%25875%25E6%259C%25881%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%258D%25B3%25E4%25BD%258D-%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25A6%258B%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2585%2583%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%2598%25AF%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE&d=emraIeL7nabu%2FhUr1ikBlE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=771a8b2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/267879/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%96%B0%E5%A4%A9%E7%9A%875%E6%9C%881%E6%97%A5%E5%8D%B3%E4%BD%8D-%E9%A6%96%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%83%E8%A6%8B%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%83%E9%A6%96%E5%B0%87%E6%98%AF%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE</a><br />\n<br />\n日本富士電視台周三（5日）報道，日美政府正就特朗普訪日事宜協調，預料屆時日本會以國賓待遇接待他。特朗普之後6月底預料還會出席在大阪舉行的二十國集團（G20）首腦峰會。換言之，特朗普有可能罕見地在短短兩個月內兩訪日本。<br />\n<br />\n《日本經濟新聞》引述日本政府消息人士表示，首相安倍晉三曾多次向特朗普試問5月訪日的可能。據稱特朗普稱對於獲得邀請表示「很榮幸」。之後兩人上周五（11月30日）在阿根廷舉行日美首腦會談時，特朗普也表示「期待與天皇陛下相關的精彩活動」，顯示他有意出訪。<br />\n<br />\n現年84歲天皇明仁早在2016年就提出因年事已高想退位，政府於2017年底正式確認其退位日期。這是日本近代首次出現天皇生前退位。而新天皇正式即位儀式則預定10月22日舉行，屆時將會邀請各國元首出席。"},{"pid":"cd435497b8a181dee880ebb0c7e3d621ead1df20","tid":930572,"uid":173631,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T11:47:16.000Z","msg":"中國天皇習近平！<br />\n<img src=\"http://scd.cn.rfi.fr/sites/chinese.filesrfi/dynimagecache/0/251/1889/1068/1024/578/sites/images.rfi.fr/files/aef_image/2017-10-25t053817z_428382468_rc1c813bc140_rtrmadp_3_china-congress.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fscd.cn.rfi.fr%2Fsites%2Fchinese.filesrfi%2Fdynimagecache%2F0%2F251%2F1889%2F1068%2F1024%2F578%2Fsites%2Fimages.rfi.fr%2Ffiles%2Faef_image%2F2017-10-25t053817z_428382468_rc1c813bc140_rtrmadp_3_china-congress.jpg&h=c932dfbe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"99918d7be0247b9ce0a38da78f1bbf66152630d2","tid":930572,"uid":199590,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T11:47:21.000Z","msg":"第一件事當然係同美國打好關係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n支那?wfc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c88a37ce1b26a040e0decef0b7efeb2fab9174c9","tid":930572,"uid":78143,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T11:57:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MzEqum5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMzEqum5.png&h=b9c6192b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"baa3f0dd8c677fe329f1f4d2e219345f7352b639","tid":930572,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd435497b8a181dee880ebb0c7e3d621ead1df20","tid":930572,"uid":173631,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T11:47:16.000Z","msg":"中國天皇習近平！<br />\n<img src=\"http://scd.cn.rfi.fr/sites/chinese.filesrfi/dynimagecache/0/251/1889/1068/1024/578/sites/images.rfi.fr/files/aef_image/2017-10-25t053817z_428382468_rc1c813bc140_rtrmadp_3_china-congress.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fscd.cn.rfi.fr%2Fsites%2Fchinese.filesrfi%2Fdynimagecache%2F0%2F251%2F1889%2F1068%2F1024%2F578%2Fsites%2Fimages.rfi.fr%2Ffiles%2Faef_image%2F2017-10-25t053817z_428382468_rc1c813bc140_rtrmadp_3_china-congress.jpg&h=c932dfbe&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T12:10:23.000Z","msg":"支那土皇帝呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afad6295ec794620d90d52171b38e26e2f16e059","tid":930572,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T12:19:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a3686884c8f796c95ee963f0e28db14e7c0c9b2d","tid":930572,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T00:52:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}